<subSubSection id="C3216524FFDBFFA6FF43FEBAFCB8FDB3" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8436AFFFDBFFA6FF43FEBAFCB8FDB3" blockId="2.[136,1452,299,578]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FF43FEBAFEA6FEB7" author="Saint-Hilaire, A." box="[136,365,299,326]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="289 - 295" refId="ref8353" refString="Saint-Hilaire, A. (1828) LXVI Luhea Willd. Flora Brasiliae meridionalis 1 (8): 289 - 295." type="journal article" year="1828">Saint-Hilaire (1828)</bibRefCitation>
did not mention a particular specimen to describe 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FC75FEBDFB9AFEB4" authorityName="Saint-Hilaire" authorityYear="1828" box="[958,1105,299,325]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="densiflora">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FC75FEBDFB9AFEB4" box="[958,1105,299,325]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. densiflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and three original specimens collected by him are in P and MPU, both repositories of his collection (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FC7EFEDEFB75FE98" author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[949,1214,335,362]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 1064). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FAA9FEDEFF18FE7F" author="Cunha, M. C. S." pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry id="F32C763FFFDBFFA6FAA9FEDEFA60FE98" box="[1378,1451,335,361]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
indicated a “not seen 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFDBFFA6FE16FEE2FD89FE7C" box="[477,578,371,397]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">holotype</typeStatus>
” at P, without specifying its identification number. 
<location id="8EE46074FFDBFFA6FB54FEE2FB16FE7C" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:039287B9FFDBFFA6FF43FF0EFCB8FDB3:8EE46074FFDBFFA6FB54FEE2FB16FE7C" box="[1183,1245,371,397]" country="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" municipality="We" name="Since" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Since</location>
<specimenCount id="9D3DFD26FFDBFFA6FB23FEE5FAB5FE7F" box="[1256,1406,372,398]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">two syntypes</specimenCount>
are present in P, the inadvertent typification by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FDB7FE06FCD3FE43" author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[636,792,407,434]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry id="F32C763FFFDBFFA6FDB7FE06FD0EFE40" box="[636,709,407,433]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
can be considered a first-step typification, and it requires now a second-step lectotypification (Art. 9.17 of the ICN). 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BE0ACD5FFDBFFA6FCE8FE2DFC83FE27" box="[803,840,444,470]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">We</collectingMunicipality>
can now designate herein specimen P 
<date id="FF85106FFFDBFFA6FB38FE2DFAA8FE27" box="[1267,1379,444,470]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" value="2937-02-14">
<collectingDate id="EFC1E987FFDBFFA6FB38FE2DFAA8FE27" box="[1267,1379,444,470]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" value="2937-02-14">02142937</collectingDate>
</date>
as the second-step 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFDBFFA6FED9FE4EFEB2FE08" box="[274,377,479,505]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">lectotype</typeStatus>
by choosing the best-preserved specimen in accordance with the protologue’s description. Based on the type materials and original descriptions, the application of the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FC19FD95FBA9FDEC" authorityName="Saint-Hilaire" authorityYear="1828" box="[978,1122,515,541]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="densiflora">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FC19FD95FBA9FDEC" box="[978,1122,515,541]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. densiflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is confirmed as a heterotypic synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDBFFA6FEDFFDB9FE59FDB0" authorityName="Willdenow" authorityYear="1801" box="[276,402,552,577]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDBFFA6FEDFFDB9FE59FDB0" box="[276,402,552,577]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. speciosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as already accepted by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDBFFA6FD6FFDB6FCA4FDB3" author="Schumann, K." box="[676,879,551,578]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="117 - 200" refId="ref8376" refString="Schumann, K. (1886) Tilliaceae. Flora Brasiliensis, enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum: quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas 12 (3): 117 - 200. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 454" type="journal article" year="1886">Schumann (1886)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
